data.description:
Welcome to the Charles F. Dodge City Center – Your Premier Event Destination!

Discover a world of possibilities for your next event at the Charles F. Dodge City Center, where sophistication meets versatility. Our state-of-the-art venue is the perfect canvas for creating unforgettable experiences, whether you're planning a corporate conference, a gala celebration, a trade show, or a social gathering. 
Nestled in the heart of Pembroke Pines, our center offers an unparalleled setting designed to elevate your event to new heights.

Explore Our Exceptional Spaces-The Great Hall, Conference Rooms and our expansive Outdoor Patio.

Why Choose Charles F. Dodge City Center- From its contemporary architecture to its cutting-edge facilities, the Charles F. Dodge City Center is more than just a venue; it's an embodiment of innovation and excellence. With a commitment to providing exceptional service, we ensure every aspect of your event is flawlessly executed, from planning to execution.

Prime Location: Centrally located in Pembroke Pines, our venue offers easy accessibility for your guests, making it convenient for both local and out-of-town attendees.

Flexible Spaces: Our range of spaces can be tailored to suit your event's unique requirements, ensuring that your vision comes to life exactly as you envision it from stadium seating, to round tables or open floor plan!

Advanced Technology: Stay ahead in the digital age with our advanced audiovisual capabilities, including high-speed internet, state-of-the-art sound systems, and projection equipment.

Expert Team: Our experienced event professionals are dedicated to assisting you throughout the planning process, guaranteeing a seamless and stress-free experience.

Parking: We have a large free parking area on site so your guests can easily park and walk up to the venue.

Elevate your event at the Charles F. Dodge City Center, where every detail is designed to make your occasion extraordinary.
